程序包org.springframework.http.server的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • 所有程序包

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.http.server.PathContainer.Options
    • org.springframework.http.server.ServletServerHttpAsyncRequestControl (implements javax.servlet.AsyncListener, org.springframework.http.server.ServerHttpAsyncRequestControl)
    • org.springframework.http.server.ServletServerHttpRequest (implements org.springframework.http.server.ServerHttpRequest)
    • org.springframework.http.server.ServletServerHttpResponse (implements org.springframework.http.server.ServerHttpResponse)

接口分层结构

  • java.lang.AutoCloseable
    • java.io.Closeable
      • org.springframework.http.server.ServerHttpResponse (并 extends java.io.Flushable, org.springframework.http.HttpOutputMessage)
  • java.io.Flushable
    • org.springframework.http.server.ServerHttpResponse (并 extends java.io.Closeable, org.springframework.http.HttpOutputMessage)
  • org.springframework.http.HttpMessage
    • org.springframework.http.HttpInputMessage
      • org.springframework.http.server.ServerHttpRequest (并 extends org.springframework.http.HttpRequest)
    • org.springframework.http.HttpOutputMessage
      • org.springframework.http.server.ServerHttpResponse (并 extends java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable)
    • org.springframework.http.HttpRequest
      • org.springframework.http.server.ServerHttpRequest (并 extends org.springframework.http.HttpInputMessage)
  • org.springframework.http.server.PathContainer
    • org.springframework.http.server.RequestPath
  • org.springframework.http.server.PathContainer.Element
    • org.springframework.http.server.PathContainer.PathSegment
    • org.springframework.http.server.PathContainer.Separator
  • org.springframework.http.server.ServerHttpAsyncRequestControl
